252
00:21:41.718 --> 00:21:43.803
[Nicole] Hmm.

253
00:21:43.803 --> 00:21:46.347
[Singer vocalizing]

254
00:21:46.347 --> 00:21:49.350
[eerie whispering]

255
00:21:49.350 --> 00:21:56.357
