These are happy tears.

1113
01:28:38.063 --> 01:28:40.065
See?

1114
01:28:40.065 --> 01:28:43.944
I'm so sorry I didn't
pick you up from school.

1115
01:28:43.944 --> 01:28:45.612
I'm so sorry.

1116
